graph LR
    KubeRay[KubeRay Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    KubeRay -->|container orchestration| K8s[Kubernetes 1.21+]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    KubeRay -.->|webhook certs| CertManager[cert-manager 1.0+]
    KubeRay -.->|GCS fault tolerance| Redis[External Redis 6.x+]
    KubeRay -.->|gang scheduling| Volcano[Volcano 1.x]
    KubeRay -.->|batch scheduling| YuniKorn[YuniKorn 1.x]
    KubeRay -.->|job queuing| Kueue[Kueue 0.x]

    %% Monitoring
    Prometheus[Prometheus 2.x] -->|scrapes metrics| KubeRay
    Grafana[Grafana 7.x+] -->|visualizes| Prometheus

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    KubeRay -->|creates routes| OpenShiftAPI[OpenShift API]
    KubeRay -->|security context| OpenShiftSCC[OpenShift SCC]
    KubeRay -.->|UI integration| ODHDashboard[ODH Dashboard]

    %% Integration Points
    RayCluster[Ray Clusters<br/>Managed Resources] -->|created by| KubeRay
    RayCluster -->|pulls images| Registry[Container Registry]
    RayCluster -->|fetches code/data| Storage[Git/S3/GCS]
    RayCluster -->|package dependencies| PyPI[Ray Package Index]

    %% Scheduling Integration
    RayCluster -.->|pod annotations| Volcano
    RayCluster -.->|pod annotations| YuniKorn
    RayCluster -.->|pod labels| Kueue

    %% External Services Access
    RayCluster -.->|external GCS| Redis

